Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • production.line.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Item
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioPlayer, MoviePlayer, Widget

    public abstract class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements Item
    Create an abstract type called Product that will implement the Item interface. Product will implement the basic functionality that all items on a production line should have. Add the following fields to Product: an id, item type, item name, and manufacturer name.
